{{For|the monster from which this item drops|Slimes|R=This page is for the item drop.}}
'''Slime''' is a [[Monster Loot]] item which is dropped by [[Slimes]]. Killing a single [[Slimes|Slime]] can drop up to two Slime. Slime can also be obtained from [[Slime Ball]]s or purchased from [[Krobus]] for {{price|10}} on [[Days of the Week#Monday|Mondays]] (up to 50 per Monday).  It may randomly appear in the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|15}}. A [[Slimejack]] [[Fish Pond]] may also produce 10, 30, or 50 Slime daily when the population reaches 9.

