==Tailoring==
Slime is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create a [[Tailoring|Shirt]]. [[File:Shirt096.png|24px]]

==Quests==
*20 Slime are requested by [[Slimejack]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 1 to 3.
*5 Slime may be requested by [[Bullhead]], [[Largemouth Bass]], or [[Midnight Carp]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 3 to 5.

==History==
{{History|1.4|[[Sturdy Ring]] now uses 25 Slime to craft.  Slime can now be used in Tailoring. Can be requested in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]]. Can be produced by Fish Ponds.}}
{{History|1.5|Added Monster Musk recipe.}}

